snippet.textDisplay:
Well done to all at the Yogscast. It was the best yet I reckon. I know there’s been some changes this past year and I’m sad that they had to happen. But the current team are still just as fun to watch. I’ve been subbed for a while, sometime half way through the Jaffa series. It’s been nice seeing more of Simon again as well.

Keep being the Yogscast and we’ll be here to watch as always :)

That being said, I wouldn’t say no to a new MC series around a new (or even old) mod pack and would be great to see the Senate back in TTT.

All in all. A brilliant year and looking forward to another one to come.

All the best and thanks lads and lasses.
